{
  "stem": "1419.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you know, like I-- like I said, that we used to get some weekly potatoes or some, some-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what do you call-- coal or wood to-- to burn, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We get some help.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe sometimes some flour, you know, from, from Polacks, from our farmers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't-- I didn't mean that they give it for nothing, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We used to-- like I say, we had textiles, and my mother had some money, and we used to buy from them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was still good that we could get from them, because everything, you know, was-- it was rationed and you couldn't get anything unless-- you know, whatever you got.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they were not allowed to sell it exactly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So [INAUDIBLE] it was help for us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They helped us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I wouldn't say that everybody got help [? us? ] and everybody did help every Polack.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But some of them did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A year and a half.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A year and a half.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then where did you go?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to Rabka, which is another resort north of, of Nowy Targ.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Zakopane used to be south of, of, of Nowy Targ, and this is north of Nowy Targ.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't go there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were sent by the Judenrat after Zakopane to go to Rabka.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Rabka is a-- like I said, a resort town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think it was for people which, which they suffered from, from diabetes or something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had some, some kind of minerals or something-- Rabka, before the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Rabka had a school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It used to be a, a Polish school for, for girls.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took it over, and they-- and they formed-- they called it [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a school strictly for Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
